<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Isu hehpihna chun,
 Mangthai chate ei hun sam hi;
 Kei di'n a thisan lul a luong tai
 Mangthai chate ei hukdamna dingin.

[V2]
 Aw athukin a sang na e,
 Gilote kala khaikang ui;
 Bang ati a him van Lal Chapa,
 Kei migilo dinga a hung thih.?

[V3]
 2. Gilo pen le ei hukdam tai,
 Liengvai gammang haw cheng a di'n;
 Gilo mun thim pen le a hih thieng,
 Aw a deih chengchengte haw hung tau uo.

[V4]
 3. Migilo chate tatna di'n,
 Bang a tia Lal lopi pen;
 Gan an kuong leh thing Kraws khelah maw.
 Aw a thukin Aw a sang ngei ie maw?

[V5]
 4. Namtin chitin te hung tau uo,
 Thamuonna leh lawpna pen chu;
 I Lal Isun ei hun piekit tai,
 A gam hawih nuom ah ei puilut ina.</lyrics>
<title>Lalpa Isu Hehpihna Chun</title>
</song>